text: Ulrich Hahnen (10 May 1952 in Krefeld - 10 January 2016) was a German politician. He was a member of the Social Democratic Party (SPD). He served as a deputy of the Landtag of North Rhine-Westphalia from 2010 until his death. In 1994, he became a member of the City Council of Krefeld, North Rhine- Westphalia. Hahnen died from cancer on 10 January 2016 at the age of 63. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Politicians from North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Politicians of the Social Democratic Party of Germany
